value: Completed education of the population aged 15 and older by county and settlement type for 2011 and  2022.

To download data:
Click on the url -> Dimensions drag them to columns,rows or sections", -> In columns drag "Census year" and "Types of settlement", "Sex", and In rows drag  "county, region" and  "Age group ", "Highest level of education completed" -> accordingly it creates table  -> click download.
